Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.41,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0015,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who the hell slashed my tires?\NWhat a cheap thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd better not be scratched...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.\NI can't find any trace of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that this\Nplace was suspicious anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fax?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Ogami's being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check to see if we\Ncan get backup! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Leave the\Ndeliveries for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy, I can't get a hold\Nof the Sagamihara office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I haven't had any word\Nfrom Taguchi since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taguchi and his team...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found their bodies\Nat our bokuto lumber yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be heading to the station\Ntomorrow for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my best to avoid charges\Nregarding an employer's duties...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...under the Anti-Organized\NCrime Law. I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their style of fighting isn't that of\Nthe Mafia. It's like that of an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. That's why they call\Nher Captain. I miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving into the final\Nstages of crushing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Washimine Clan's locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sites 371 and 372\Nhave been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daniel's team is currently\Nheaded for site 221.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will commence at 1505 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Corporal Razal\Nmet his objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're tied up in traffic\Non the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they should still\Nmeet the activation time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okchabri-skiajin This{\i0}\N{\i1}is Corporal Jodorowsky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed our objectives\Nwithin the planned time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now be withdrawing\Nfrom our operation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger. Return to base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Site 215 is under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The death of officer Shigeru Ito\Nhas been confirmed at site 317.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Good work, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In three more moves the Princess\Nwill be completely stripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a hold of the Sis.\NWe're done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says we've got\Nanother job tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You look gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you're having\Na good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been together for so long,\NI guess you can tell these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting a guy like that\Nsurely makes a gunman happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it, baby?\NHe sliced a bullet right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It blew my mind all the way to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to have a duel\Nwith that big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What benefit is there in\Nrushing yourself to your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rushing myself to my death?\NYou're missing the point, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already the walking dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, the Sis, Chang,\Nand the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us running around in Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's one difference\Nbetween us and the real dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we live or die\Nisn't a big issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you focus on being alive, you\Ndevelop fear. Your eyes get clouded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you have no such feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're capable of fighting\Nright to the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you prefer to\Ndie in the gutter like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow Roanapur\Nfeels so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rock. What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure snapping\Nback at me a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry. Drinking's bringing out\Nthe worst in me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, you mustn't go\Naround teasing adults like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Nbrought up the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it's conditional that the\Nsuccessor be a direct blood relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has been acknowledged\Nby the Peacekeeping Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't fool with me, you little brat!\N- Shut up, Morozumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on allowing\Nyou to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what are\Nyou gonna do about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those crazy Russians\Nyou brought in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you say,\Nthat's an error on our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire Washimine Clan is\Ndoing everything we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to expel those Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing the point,\NWashimine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm asking is how are you gonna\Nrepay us for all that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but you haven't\Nforgotten the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why our last boss, Bando...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...took this desperate measure,\Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was some grudge\Nyou had against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We even sent you\Na replacement head...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to try and protect\Nour brother organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who turned that down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. We shall eventually settle\Nthis with the Peacekeeping Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat! You're in over your head,\Ntaking a position like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Peacekeeping Council has the\Nauthority to direct mediation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we have gathered enough\Nmaterial to justify our actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given Boss Kousa's attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it may be useless to get\Nthe Peacekeeping Council involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in this world\Nare all controlled by greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear which side would be\Nmore beneficial for them to support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the painful reminder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the current\NWashimine Clan is only...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one-third the force we had\Nat the start of the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Russians' attacks\Nare too severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They started by targeting\Nand eliminating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the guys heading our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're still here. You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Inoue.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Please send a message\Nto everyone who is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow those who have\Nbeen protecting Washimine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be eliminated at this point.\NAnd that includes you, Mr. Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will create\Nan opportunity on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please stay alive and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will not\Nlet things end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, every group's\Noffice entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is protected with\Na surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although heavily damaged, this is\Na video tape that survived the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I succeeded in taking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before the police closed\Noff the place for investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving around in\Nelectric repair shop vans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we knew where these\Ncars were coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy the police for\Nthat N-system they use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a thrill to be a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Bonnie and Clyde!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, we're gonna\Nrob a bank in Bolivia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A robbery has occurred at the credit{\i0}\N{\i1}union on the fourth block of Inoue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two suspects{\i0}\N{\i1}are escaping by car.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A white van with a red{\i0}\N{\i1}spade mark on the side door.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All patrol cars in the area,{\i0}\N{\i1}be on the lookout. I repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That world that Mr. Okajima\Nis standing on the border of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a city where only\Ngangsters gather and live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a Yakuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...making a name for\Nhimself in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the city is Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Balalaika's\Nfrom there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking how great it would be\Nif life in Takamachi would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With musical bands, all the stores,\Nand you by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's bound to be enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is... This is\Neven more fun than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we're gonna have\Nto deal with the Russian lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we're gonna live in that city.\NThis is gonna be exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is patrol car Shinagawa 142.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We spotted a van with a red spade{\i0}\N{\i1}heading north along the shoreline.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We ordered them to pull over,{\i0}\N{\i1}but they picked up speed instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}We need reinforcements.{\i0}\N- We've got them, Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shoreline... Close to Tokyo Port...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Jodorowsky.\NWe're being chased by a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lose them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balalaika. They came\Nfrom Roanapur. But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all those\Nweapons and equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could never get through\Nan airport. Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship? Balalaika's at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost them. We'll get rid\Nof the car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? How did the police find\Nout what car we were using?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that girl challenging me with\Nher first effective countermeasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing. We'll just have to\Ncrush her especially thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledge exists so that\Nwe may forget reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intoxication of reality\Nthat cannot be found in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A land that symbolizes that,\NRoanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. With Balalaika away,\Nthis place is falling to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of gunshots\Nhas gone up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triad's doing a pretty good\Njob keeping things together, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gun paradise, Benny.\NThat's the true appearance of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang really understands\Nthat about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing Rock's not here.\NGuns are just not his thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta realize that\None of our biggest blessings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the fact Rock hasn't\Nhad to hold a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fires, his bullets will\Nricochet right back at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too damned dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious, man. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry I made you wait.\N- Not to worry. So what's the next job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another meeting with the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can finalize this sufficiently,\Nwe can return to Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meeting?\NBut the Washimine Clan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people we're talking\Nto now are the Kousa Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will get rid of all of our troubles.\NIt'll be very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you don't{\i0}\N{\i1}actually want to save me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't want to lose that normal{\i0}\N{\i1}life that you thought you threw away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}That's all.{\i0}\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as what they have to say\Nisn't insulting, maybe we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...consider one of their conditions.\N- Hey, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to stay in the{\i0}\N{\i1}twilight like that again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to ally\Nyourself with the Kousa Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than destroying the Washimine\NClan, you'd be better off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...destroying the Kousa Clan.\N- Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Washimine Clan\Nis already weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer a threat to Moscow.\NAm I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And the Washimine Group's...\N- Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand your position.\NYou are my interpreter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my fellow soldier, comrade,\Nor a member of Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new leader of the Washimine\NClan is still a teenager!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Let's stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a justice\Nthat you believe in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Rock.\NYou're being a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all calm down, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna reenact a scene from\N"My Bloody Valentine" here, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop howling, Revy.\NRock, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other word\Nmore loved by the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful word. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without exercising\Nyour own strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you seek the death of others\Nby the hands of someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The justice you refer to\Nsmells pretty rotten too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stench of a bloodbath lingers.\NDon't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.\NI'm not upset with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just never thought I'd hear\Nwords like that coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so amused, I can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made your point.\NNow let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers are getting tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives are very insignificant.\NMuch like a candy wrapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yours is, and so is his.\N- I don't really care to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Hands, I have something\Nto say to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you should not wish for\Nthe same way of life as his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know what you're saying.\NSo please, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep my fingers\Nstill for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Balalaika.\NYour victory is assured...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you no longer have\Nanything to lose. Yet still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rock.\N- Is it still not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, there are two successful\Nways to beg for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is to entertain the person\Nwho's about to take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other is to give that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a persuasive reason to\Nkeep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fulfilled either one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What obligation do you have\Nto save them, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh?\N- It's not an obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And justice is\Njust a convenient word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one reason.\NIt's my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people consider it\Na hobby to die in the gutters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then there\Nare hobbies like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down inside, I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are gonna pick\Nup again tomorrow, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you'd be wise not to\Nrisk your life on stupid games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Park the car in the garage, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason we're\Nstill breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because of God's grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the fact that the\Ncrazy war maniac in the coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for some reason decided\Nto put her gun away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah sure, I'm your gun here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident I can protect you\Nthrough Tarawa or the Alamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, it's just not\Npossible to protect a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who's trying damn hard\Nto get killed, you blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you mad?\N- Not even close. I'm damn pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't you, I would've shot\Ntwo or three holes into you by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask. Will you\Ncome to my town one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to have the Sis tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your place is a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got a little lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so far away,\Nthere's no way I could reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I've lived my life\Nbreathing rotten air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had even forgotten that I don't\Nknow how to live anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's just the Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always had her eyes\Nset only on war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, and never look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to wake\Nup from your nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Have you forgotten?\NI'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I died that day I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Roanapur is the city of the walking\Ndead, this is the city of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being so familiar with this view,\NI had almost forgotten that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a dead man,\Nthis is like a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This may have been a mirage\Neven back when I lived here. Revy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here to return\Nto my former life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to keep watching\Neverything that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished regretting a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't have enough resolve,\Nbut now I think I've got that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's the lady from\Nthe other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you show us what\Nyou did last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, shoot those cans\Ndown again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on a show for them, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of gun is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here's a Beretta M92 Custom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Praiyachat Sword\NCutlass Special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now watch those cans\Ncarefully, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cans,\Nwatch them close, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mommy's waiting for you.\NNow go home you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin. I'd like to have\Na more powerful gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be one in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very familiar with projectiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's apparently a\NRussian "Stechkin" handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the bullets are big and\Nit can keep firing like a machine gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be too much for you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to be less of a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:18.56,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This city, Roanapur...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful place...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where you can blow away\Neverything with barbaric power.
